# Simple XML to JSON transformation

%utlx 1.0
input xml
output json
---
{
  person: {
    name: input.Person.Name,
    age: parseNumber(input.Person.Age),
    email: input.Person.Email
  }
}

# Run with XML input:
# <Person>
#   <Name>Alice</Name>
#   <Age>30</Age>
#   <Email>alice@example.com</Email>
# </Person>

---
